Police in Suba, Homa Bay County, are hunting for a group of daring robbers who made an attempt to steal from the office of the Directorate of Criminal Investigations (DCI) and the sub-county treasury office on Sunday night.
The robbers failed to break into the two offices but managed to steal valuables from another office and local shops within Magunga trading centre.



